post.description:
Deduct inventory for an order.
Called when order status changes to 'preparing'.

Expected data:
{
    "orderId": "order_123",
    "items": [
        {"name": "Chicken Biryani", "quantity": 2, "menuItemId": "item_123"},
        {"name": "Margherita Pizza", "quantity": 1, "menuItemId": "item_456"}
    ]
}

Handle order ready - chef finished preparing and marked order as ready
Updates table status to 'served' immediately

Expected data:
{
    "orderId": "order_id"
}

Handle bill generation - bill is created for the table

Expected data:
{
    "orderId": "order_id",
    "billId": "bill_id",
    "totalAmount": 500.00,
    "billDetails": {...}
}
